author: Ryan George Extra Plus!
description:
With everything that's going on in the world today it's easy to miss out on some of the more absurd news headlines that really make you wonder how we've made it this far. Nuking the ocean to save the world, 14 million escaped honeybees, flying sharks? All that and more in today's episode of It's Weird Out There.
